{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"344c71fed6","title":"关于增产节约的讲话（记录稿）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e5ac3f5ad3","index":0,"year":1955,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"344c71fed6"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5377c7d466","type":"title","text":"关于增产节约的讲话（记录稿）","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"0ab556ede9","type":"paragraph","text":"我们是人口众多、经济落后的大国，经济水平、生活水平均很低，建设社会主义，十五年内是过渡时期，中心是工业化，打物质基础。在现有条件下，继续贯彻党的限苦奋斗传统。资金唯一来源靠自己积累。第一个五年十个指头，只做了一个。第二、三个五年资金需要更天，不历行节约无法完成任务。如果非生产建设投资突出了，会破坏工农联盟和全国团结，农民为什么不进城？十五年内，不可能样样现代化，样样社会主义，是打基础阶段。非重点建设，非近代技术装备的工厂，第一个五年感到困难，第二、第三个更要大。削国防不可能，削行政人员，也非安置生产，非加强生产不可。不可设想削减建设国防人员解决问题。只有全面节约解决问","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"0408ff8920","type":"subtitle","text":"题。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"72259c9c8f","type":"paragraph","text":"过去认识不深，贯彻不透。如工厂，福利设施均社会主义设施。已无福利可增加。先抓生产、开工","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"e7b1551df7","type":"paragraph","text":"农场也太近代化了。牛场120万平方米，先进社会。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"86ed9f8656","type":"paragraph","text":"工房、宿舍、高楼、大厦，百把万，住不起。长春汽车厂、乌拉尔厂，宿舍太漂亮了。厨房，西太后出来也要说话了。这是不了解建设困难，忘记传统，违背工业化方针及与农民共限苦患难的","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"60a66660b4","type":"subtitle","text":"精神。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"5f8dbf00a5","type":"paragraph","text":"生产和生活不平衡。节约为了增加积累。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"f9dfa643f1","type":"paragraph","text":"一、除近代化技术设备以及和设备必要配合的厂房（国外的按国外设计，国内的按可能削减），其他一律降低造价。和延安窑洞看齐，办公室、教室、农场、宿舍、车站等按过渡时期标准，用十五年、二十年。一律砖木结构，甚至土坯子、竹泥墙。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"d3b34dd89a","type":"paragraph","text":"一类是现有大城市，可以砖木。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"99a3a89024","type":"paragraph","text":"二类新的单独城市、厂矿，要用土坯","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"132377ed9b","type":"paragraph","text":"办公室、学校50元至70元","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"53f84596c6","type":"paragraph","text":"宿舍20元至50元","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"558ba66cd8","type":"paragraph","text":"不同宿舍不同房租。","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"04222dfb6d","type":"paragraph","text":"仓库40元至50元","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"ad16d2cf3d","type":"paragraph","text":"车站50元至70元","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"355c79799c","type":"paragraph","text":"首都盖大楼装样子，须国务院批准。","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"81fbc0fd00","type":"paragraph","text":"工程部六至八月拟出标准。","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"2f7caef0e5","type":"paragraph","text":"二、新建工厂、铁道、农场、福利、设施，根据生产、利润、业务的情况，逐年实施。先抓重点，如宿舍、卫生所无利润以前不建设。不可一下子社会主义，是远景，不是一下子社会主义。首先礼堂不可搞。","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"598fe2e6bf","type":"paragraph","text":"三、新建企业其他方面厉行节约。轻工业至多一年的筹备机关，以前筹备由部局直接筹备。","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"d8ca1f3a15","type":"paragraph","text":"设计，照标准。重工业部门到苏联的人太多。","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"15ae54ed26","type":"paragraph","text":"实习生的待遇要降低","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"fbf6f5a1c5","type":"paragraph","text":"每个环节，严加控制。厂内办公室，沙发一律不准，也不买收音机。不要厂长和职工生活脱离太远。","index":22,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"ef59b54f56","type":"paragraph","text":"四、现有新城，计划均要修改，不要搞社会主义化，要利用旧城。工业要相当疏散","index":23,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"97f989b77b","type":"paragraph","text":"1.不搞高大建筑。一层两层","index":24,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"28c08717a9","type":"paragraph","text":"2.非工业集中的城市，根本不建城市。如职工用水，可用地下水，用自来水者使用公共水龙头","index":25,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"a16aad9ca5","type":"paragraph","text":"马路要，绿化面积慢慢来。","index":26,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"f560420af1","type":"paragraph","text":"先工业化，后“社会主义化”。二十年后，再用新规划","index":27,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"e01501f09d","type":"paragraph","text":"五、今年准备建筑的高楼大厂，未动工的一律停止。","index":28,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"891a878f1a","type":"paragraph","text":"六、地质勘探","index":29,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"f6e71228a9","type":"paragraph","text":"1.勘探量不必增加。","index":30,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"1f66d8a590","type":"paragraph","text":"2.希望增加的，增加50%工作量。","index":31,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"294bca23f4","type":"paragraph","text":"七、建筑部六、七、八个月交出标准。","index":32,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"637a8d1e94","type":"paragraph","text":"1.生产方面：","index":33,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"4160f9c8b6","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）降低成本：工业6%加到7.5%；铁路2.5%至3.5%；商业2.9%至13.9%。","index":34,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"5809bbf9f8","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）节约原料，轻工业、棉花、卷烟量。","index":35,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"96720ad1a2","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）重工业完成新产品试制计划，上半年49%，不及一半。","index":36,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"0bfa0daa3b","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）一律停止收新工人，先内部清理调整，现在都核不清。现在人多了。","index":37,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"a99ae910ab","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）每一环节，直至清理垃圾。鞍钢月搞五万吨钢铁，指标到车间。","index":38,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"fbffe640fd","type":"paragraph","text":"2.生活消费：","index":39,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"eb1418cd64","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）除招待外宾外，一律只供清茶一杯，一律不请客、会餐。","index":40,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"81f787ead3","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）办公室不买沙发，首长办公室，两个小沙发，用会议桌。","index":41,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"146b9031db","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）公文表报节约，非国家统计局批不可发。","index":42,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"},{"id":"3b965f29aa","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）减少汽车使用。","index":43,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6"}],"page":{"id":"3494c9179f","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"344c71fed6","start":123,"end":125}}}},"__N_SSG":true}